window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Once upon a time, I was your average spunky redhead with the lamest employment history ever, a shaky relationship with my only family member, and no idea what I was doing with my life.&nbsp;</p> <p>Now, I'm a pseudo mythic with the best bartending job in the world, the most amazing (and hot) best friends I never knew I needed, and a guild of misfit magic users who've become my extended family.&nbsp;</p> <p>And I'm about to lose it all.&nbsp;</p> <p>In my desperation to save Ezra, I stumbled into a web of ruthless deception - and seriously pissed off a sleeping hydra. Now its every murderous head is turned toward me and my guild, and I don't know how to stop it. I'm not sure I can.&nbsp;</p> <p>I'm not sure anyone can.&nbsp;</p> <p>But if we don't, we're all doomed - Ezra, Aaron, Kai, and my beloved guild.</p>"; 
